Suggests: secubox-soc-gateway
Description: SecuBox SOC Web Dashboard — Browser-based Fleet Monitoring
 React-based web dashboard for the SecuBox Security Operations Center.
 Provides real-time fleet monitoring, alert visualization, and remote
 node management through a modern web interface.
 .
 Features:
  - Fleet overview with node health grid
  - Real-time alert stream via WebSocket
  - Cross-node threat correlation visualization
  - Remote service management (start/stop/restart)
  - Threat intelligence map
  - Cyberpunk-themed responsive UI
 .
 Part of the SecuBox hierarchical SOC architecture.
